Cyber Claw:





Cyber Claw shook her head at Serpentor, as he fell to the ground. He called 
her an Autobot. An Autobot? There was something clearly wrong with his head. 
He was no good to her.

She spun around to see an flier charge at her and fire. She ducked, flying 
to the side. This one might do, she mused. She returned fire with twin green 
lazer from her optics.
